reviewText: I was very pleased with my purchase,sure the disk isn't a original but the quality of it is perfect and it comes packed with 5 episodes including one I've never seen back in the day which I would call the origin of freddy, which I would say is the best one.  Im waiting for more episodes to become available for purchase.
